{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.1","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:1","prev_osis_id":"1Thess.005.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.001.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Adresse et salutation<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-2: cf. 1 Th 1:1.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.1.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Paul, et Silvain, et Timoth\u00e9e, \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9glise des Thessaloniciens, qui est en Dieu notre P\u00e8re et en J\u00e9sus-Christ le Seigneur:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Thess.5.28","name":"1 Thessaloniciens 5:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Thess.5.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.2","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:2","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.001.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.001.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.1.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>que la gr\u00e2ce et la paix vous soient donn\u00e9es de la part de Dieu notre P\u00e8re et du Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.3","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:3","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.001.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.001.004,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Progr\u00e8s des Thessaloniciens dans la foi et dans la charit\u00e9, malgr\u00e9 les pers\u00e9cutions<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 3-10: cf. (1 Th 1:2-7. Ph 1:3-6, 27-30.) (Mt 5:10-12. Ro 8:17, 18. 1 Pi 4:12, 13.) (Mt 13:40-43; 25:31-46.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.1.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>\n    Nous devons \u00e0 votre sujet, fr\u00e8res, rendre continuellement gr\u00e2ces \u00e0 Dieu, comme cela est juste, parce que votre foi fait de grands progr\u00e8s, et que la charit\u00e9 de chacun de vous tous \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard des autres augmente de plus en plus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.4","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.4","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:4","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.001.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.001.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.1.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Aussi nous glorifions-nous de vous dans les \u00c9glises de Dieu, \u00e0 cause de votre pers\u00e9v\u00e9rance et de votre foi au milieu de toutes vos pers\u00e9cutions et des tribulations que vous avez \u00e0 supporter.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.5","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.5","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:5","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.001.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.001.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.1.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>C\u2019est une preuve du juste jugement de Dieu, pour que vous soyez jug\u00e9s dignes du royaume de Dieu, pour lequel vous souffrez.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.6","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.4","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.6","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:6","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.001.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.001.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.1.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Car il est de la justice de Dieu de rendre l\u2019affliction \u00e0 ceux qui vous affligent,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.7","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.5","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.7","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:7","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.001.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.001.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.1.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>et de vous donner, \u00e0 vous qui \u00eates afflig\u00e9s, du repos avec nous, lorsque le Seigneur J\u00e9sus appara\u00eetra du ciel avec les anges de sa puissance,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.8","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.6","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.8","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:8","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.001.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.001.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.1.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>au milieu d\u2019une flamme de feu, pour punir ceux qui ne connaissent pas Dieu et ceux qui n\u2019ob\u00e9issent pas \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9vangile de notre Seigneur J\u00e9sus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.9","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.7","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.9","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:9","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.001.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.001.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.1.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Ils auront pour ch\u00e2timent une ruine \u00e9ternelle, loin de la face du Seigneur et de la gloire de sa force,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.10","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.8","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.10","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:10","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.001.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.001.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.1.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>lorsqu\u2019il viendra pour \u00eatre, en ce jour-l\u00e0, glorifi\u00e9 dans ses saints et admir\u00e9 dans tous ceux qui auront cru, car notre t\u00e9moignage aupr\u00e8s de vous a \u00e9t\u00e9 cru.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.11","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.9","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.11","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:11","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.001.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.001.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-12: cf. Col 1:9-12. H\u00e9 13:20, 21.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.1.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi aussi nous prions continuellement pour vous, afin que notre Dieu vous juge dignes de la vocation, et qu\u2019il accomplisse par sa puissance tous les desseins bienveillants de sa bont\u00e9, et l\u2019\u0153uvre de votre foi,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.12","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.10","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.12","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:12","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.001.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.1.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>pour que le nom de notre Seigneur J\u00e9sus soit glorifi\u00e9 en vous, et que vous soyez glorifi\u00e9s en lui, selon la gr\u00e2ce de notre Dieu et du Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.11","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbba4b201.65793034');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbba4b201.65793034\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbba4b201.65793034","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbba4b201.65793034'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbba4b201.65793034\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}